{"tid":2239420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環甲廈空置率7.2% 2008年金融海嘯後的近12年新高","createTime":"2020-10-12T02:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:10:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"d873271dcc514ef209671730db294980d5b08a96","tid":2239420,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】受肺炎疫情影響，加上政治前景未明朗，本港經濟疲弱。<br />\n<br />\n美聯最新數據指，整體甲廈空置率持續上升，其中中環區相關空置率升至7.2%，屬2008年金融海嘯後的近12年新高；該區甲廈租金今年累跌23.8%，跑輸整體約19.7%的跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201012/IYJD23B3ZVAG5JCRECDINDS57U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201012%2FIYJD23B3ZVAG5JCRECDINDS57U%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=002c0647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201012%2FIYJD23B3ZVAG5JCRECDINDS57U%2F&h=8519ab1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201012/IYJD23B3ZVAG5JCRECDINDS57U/</a>"},{"pid":"c7622f2eb9b97d5ff56191632c9008973db7ef4c","tid":2239420,"uid":50386,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"又話國安法之後仲多公司嚟香港營商嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2e036dd9d0d8f55346bf2c0c98a58f22ede526","tid":2239420,"uid":281311,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:08:45.000Z","msg":"又諗起當初接中環中心班人笑鳩誠哥時嘅嘴臉"},{"pid":"b539a26470997abe40964ee44318df0b871b6f50","tid":2239420,"uid":18477,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77Tf6pH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77Tf6pH.gif&h=6057e569&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c29b89d09bcc6c125244ba0eab870e84dfd59280","tid":2239420,"uid":273218,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:11:01.000Z","msg":"一開時事台頭兩個都係樓價大跌新聞<br 